# --- Eval receipt photos + sensitive cases: real customer data — keep LOCAL ---
# The public repo must not publish real business/client data. The photos, and
# any eval case whose GROUND TRUTH is a real client name (so the label must
# match the private image), live only on the machine that has the receipts.
# The runner takes multiple --dataset files and skips image cases whose file is
# absent, so the committed text+generic-image half stays reproducible for anyone
# (see docs/EVAL_BASELINE.md).
evals/images/
evals/dataset.local.jsonl
